{"tid":2051202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港區国安法】滙豐及渣打支持国安法　英首相發言人：「深切關注」","createTime":"2020-06-04T15:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T17:20:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"df06e570d7cb2d6a516abae1c426043f4c339315","tid":2051202,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"受政治人物和內地媒體批評未表態後，香港兩大英資發鈔銀行滙豐 （00005） 及渣打 （02888） 最新表態支持訂立「港區國安法」。不過，滙豐和渣打表態後，即受到英國方面的關注。英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）發言人James Slack表示，英國政府「深切關注」滙豐和渣打的舉動。<br />\n<br />\nSlack形容，中國正處於「違背對港義務」的風險中，若港區國安法正式實施，中國將直接違背對香港的義務。Slack指出，英國政府此舉是對滙豐及渣打的直接回應。他又相信，英國目前對此議題表達的訊息「清晰」，其國際伙伴也應有相同的看法。<br />\n<br />\n香港總商會主席、香港上海匯豐銀行有限公司副主席兼行政總裁王冬勝早前接受新華社採訪，說香港商界普遍認為香港國家安全立法是一個正確方向，希望香港國家安全立法可以為香港帶來長遠的繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2661991/?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2661991%2F%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Egmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=ec44aad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2661991/?mtc=20023</a>"},{"pid":"e4fdcf60f4eaedad24b7459308902f822b179e2e","tid":2051202,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"兩邊不是人"},{"pid":"eceb49bf9706ae9b5289b5fa2bdbc5c6b9df2844","tid":2051202,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bc0fedadbc12e4b89317b117554000543f767d","tid":2051202,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfbac6e03582d717a8b02c8094fe1462cf4fce0","tid":2051202,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8144617c1c1250